name: Green Water Dive Filter (For Super Suit)

features: Provides color correction while capturing footage in green water at depths of 15 to 70ft (5 to 21m)
Constructed of scratch-resistant, optical-grade glass for optimal image clarity
Presses into place for quick, tool-free installation
Includes a tether and a microfiber bag for storage and lens cleaning
For use with Super Suit (Über Protection + Dive Housing for HERO5 Black).
